OL,3,CInflation expected to cool to two-and-
OL,4,Ca-half-year low
OL,6,FUK inflation has been predicted to
OL,7,Ffall to its lowest level since
OL,8,FSeptember 2021 when fresh economic
OL,9,Fdata is released.
OL,11,FThe Office for National Statistics is
OL,12,Fexpected to reveal on Wednesday that
OL,13,FConsumer Prices Index (CPI) inflation
OL,14,Fwas around 3.1% in March, according to
OL,15,Fa consensus of economists.
OL,17,FIt comes after a reading of 3.4% in
OL,18,FFebruary and will mark the lowest for
OL,19,Ftwo and a half years, when it was also
OL,20,F3.1%.
