OL,3,CInflation expected to cool to two-and-
OL,4,Ca-half-year low
OL,6,FEconomists at Pantheon Macroeconomics
OL,7,Fpredicted the reading could fall even
OL,8,Ffurther, with an estimate of 3%.
OL,10,FHowever, they stressed that services
OL,11,Finflation ` which has been a focus for
OL,12,FBank of England policymakers
OL,13,Fconsidering potential interest rate
OL,14,Fcuts ` is likely to remain at elevated
OL,15,Flevels.
OL,17,FPantheon says it expects services
OL,18,Finflation of 5.9% for the month,
OL,19,Fnudging down slightly from 6.1% a
OL,20,Fmonth earlier.
