OL,3,CInflation expected to cool to two-and-
OL,4,Ca-half-year low
OL,6,FRobert Wood, chief UK economist at the
OL,7,Fresearch company, said food and goods
OL,8,Fprices are expected to drop over the
OL,9,Fmonth, contributing to the slower rate
OL,10,Fof inflation.
OL,12,FHe said he expects slower services
OL,13,Finflation to "shave another 0.1
OL,14,Fpercentage points off the headline
OL,15,Finflation rate, despite a boost from
OL,16,Fthe early Easter, as last year's huge
OL,17,Fprice rises continue to drop out of
OL,18,Fthe annual comparison".
