OL,3,CInflation expected to cool to two-and-
OL,4,Ca-half-year low
OL,6,FMr Wood and Oxford Economics' Edward
OL,7,FAllenby both said the cool-down in
OL,8,Finflation means the Bank of England is
OL,9,Flikely to start cutting interest rates
OL,10,Ffrom 5.25% in June.
OL,12,FMr Allenby said inflation is expected
OL,13,Fto hit the Bank's target rate of 2%
OL,14,Flater this year, although the benefit
OL,15,Fof falling energy prices could prove
OL,16,Ftemporary and cause inflation to tip
OL,17,Fhigher again.
