OL,3,CInflation expected to cool to two-and-
OL,4,Ca-half-year low
OL,6,F"Further declines in wholesale gas
OL,7,Fprices mean the energy component
OL,8,Fshould continue to drag heavily on
OL,9,Fheadline inflation throughout 2024,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,F"Meanwhile, the food and core
OL,13,Fcategories will benefit from strong
OL,14,Fbase effects and the indirect effects
OL,15,Fof lower energy costs.
OL,17,F"Therefore, our latest forecast shows
OL,18,Finflation dropping well below 2% in
OL,19,Fthe second half of 2024."
